President Muhammadu Buhari is currently having a meeting with the Inspector General of Police, Mohammed Adamu and the Chairman of the Police Service Commission, Mr. Musiliu Smith.and the Chairman of the Police Service Commission, Mr Musiliu Smith. Smith is a former Inspector-General of Police. He came to the meeting in company with other members of the commission. The Chief of Staff to the President, Abba Kyari, is also part of the meeting. Business Hallmark gathered from a reliable source that the agenda is said to be the 2018 annual report of the PSC.